{"tid":1611294,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[食肆 TVB 商場] 制裁目標未夠清晰 要聚焦 要增強","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T05:47:35.000Z","uid":29218,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"023326b3053a8c8ba4b208ba81959ffeca709b33","tid":1611294,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:17:30.000Z","msg":"我反對直接破壞舖面 因為形象太差<br />\n變咗佢哋先係受害者<br />\n但而家制裁目標太多 亦未見好大效果<br />\n制裁分散 宣傳亦唔夠力<br />\n變咗單純破壞 失去制裁嘅意義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罷食方面<br />\n前有吉野家 麥當勞<br />\n後有美心(一大堆)<br />\n要集中制裁一個字號先有最大效用<br />\n例如今個星期要制裁美心嘅元氣<br />\n就喺每一間元氣嘅門口貼佢嘅海報(例如 魚生有蟲)<br />\n午飯晚飯時間快閃喺舖前派傳單畀每一個入去食嘅顧客<br />\n其餘店舖做法一樣 吉野家就黑龍江米<br />\n每間都實有唔好嘅新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罷TVB亦要做類似嘅嘢<br />\n因為網上負評有用 但唔夠威力<br />\n例如今個星期針對喜療疤<br />\n就去萬寧 屈臣氏<br />\n(如果係金寶湯就去百佳惠康)<br />\n掃晒啲喜療疤落地<br />\n踢到周圍都係<br />\n今個星期每日如是<br />\n最後留低標語話係因為佢喺TVB 落廣告先針對佢<br />\n最終舖頭要將tvb買廣告嘅商品全部下架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地鐵同地產商最重要係商場<br />\n每個星期(最好星期六 因為啲人星期日都唔敢再去shopping) 都要集中一間 <br />\n例如新城市<br />\n叫口號鳩嗚<br />\n破壞電梯 (最好唔好搞𨋢 如果唔係輪椅走唔到)<br />\n放下臭彈 蟲 之類<br />\n打爆啲門口啲地磚/玻璃門 (因為人客一入就見到 就唔想再幫襯)<br />\n唔使破壞舖頭 但令購物者唔想再去shopping 足矣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三方面都可以快閃<br />\n目標集中就可以有效文宣 (包括外媒)"},{"pid":"b635b0e7849016c4e5116b9371ed89ad4936fd5a","tid":1611294,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437d2c4ece717e0fb3b57baa303704f49947975b","tid":1611294,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f5d5cad528dea969b32be2b082a23527ace820","tid":1611294,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339a04ee505ab002f93c87bfb8d677818d237f91","tid":1611294,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:26:02.000Z","msg":"第一段話怕形象太差<br />\n之後果幾段做啲野形象都係好差架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係做就做 唔好怕啲咩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf943ce6768c4ccde90d3d07031cbadb6cb5088","tid":1611294,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339a04ee505ab002f93c87bfb8d677818d237f91","tid":1611294,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:26:02.000Z","msg":"第一段話怕形象太差<br />\n之後果幾段做啲野形象都係好差架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係做就做 唔好怕啲咩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"係宣傳唔集中先會形象差<br />\n人哋只係睇到我哋嘅action <br />\n唔明白我哋嘅intention<br />\n所以先要強力集中嘅文宣配合<br />\n<br />\n而家好聽就兄弟爬山<br />\n但好多不知情嘅人 就算係本地人<br />\n都一頭霧水<br />\n就係由於文宣跟唔上行動"},{"pid":"e0573fbc13c61d4037a68503b537673e8fecf1ff","tid":1611294,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a0994600ac6720c191499b6fb487e0de9f4af4","tid":1611294,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf57124ccc4c2dd7715ac3d453d7d625f13e96b","tid":1611294,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1acbf4284ef5e2a78c99247db4d2f132d5ded98","tid":1611294,"uid":236302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"美心茶狼幾時得閑搞搞佢"},{"pid":"a39ed2f30e712db948c847bc3d63b341cb2fcc12","tid":1611294,"uid":29218,"like":